<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    background-color: #1f1f1f;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

nav {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #7c3aed);
    padding: 1.3rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0.2);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-container {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.logo {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
}

.nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
}

.nav-links li a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.nav-links li a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.nav-links li a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: #059669;
    bottom: -3px;
    left: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.nav-links li a:hover::after {
    width: 60%;
}

.hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.15), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15));
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
    animation: rotate 25s linear infinite;
}

.hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: slideIn 0.9s ease-out;
}

.hero-section h1 span {
    color: #059669;
}

.hero-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeIn 1.1s ease-out;
}

.about-section {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
}

.about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
}

.about-text {
    background: #2d2d2d;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    animation: fadeInUp 1.3s ease-out;
}

.about-text h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #059669;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.about-image img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

.mission-vision {
    margin: 5rem 0;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #7c3aed);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeIn 1.7s ease-out;
}

.mission-vision h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.mission-vision p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.team-section {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.team-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: slideIn 0.9s ease-out;
}

.team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
}

.team-member {
    background: #2d2d2d;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out;
}

.team-member:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

.team-member img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 150px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.team-member h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #059669;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.team-member p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
}

.back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    color: #059669;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.back-link:hover {
    color: #7c3aed;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-30px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
    }
}

@keyframes rotate {
    from {
        transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    to {
        transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image img {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
}



    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo">MySite</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <h1>About <span>MySite</span></h1>
        <p>Discover our journey, values, and the passionate team behind innovative solutions that shape the future.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                <p>At MySite, we are a dynamic team of innovators, designers, and technologists committed to transforming ideas into reality. Founded in 2015, our journey began with a simple mission: to create meaningful digital experiences that empower our clients and their audiences.</p>
                <p>Our multidisciplinary approach combines cutting-edge technology, creative design, and strategic thinking to deliver solutions that are not only functional but also inspiring. From startups to global enterprises, we partner with organizations to drive growth and innovation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x400" alt="Team collaborating in office">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission-vision">
        <h2>Our Mission & Vision</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to empower businesses and individuals through innovative, user-centric solutions that foster creativity, collaboration, and growth. We envision a world where technology bridges gaps, connects communities, and unlocks endless possibilities for progress.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="team-section">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team member 1">
                <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
                <p>CEO & Founder</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team member 2">
                <h3>John Smith</h3>
                <p>Lead Developer</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Team member 3">
                <h3>Emily Brown</h3>
                <p>Creative Director</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>